00:09:42.206 --> 00:09:43.249  
[Wagner] No?

198
00:09:43.332 --> 00:09:46.711 
{\an8}So. um. we'll do your schedule
in the morning.

199
00:09:46.794 --> 00:09:50.715 
{\an8}just. you know. whatever we've gotta do
to get out in December. okay?

200
00:09:50.798 --> 00:09:53.092 
{\an8}-We'll figure it out.
-So will you call me on his schedule?

201
00:09:53.175 --> 00:09:55.261 
{\an8}-Ma'am?
-Will you call me on his schedule?

202
00:09:55.344 --> 00:09:56.929  
He doesn't make them decisions.

203
00:09:57.722 --> 00:09:59.015  
-[Wagner] I'll handle it.
-Okay.

204
00:09:59.098 --> 00:10:00.224  
[Wagner] I won't leave it up to him.

205
00:10:00.307 --> 00:10:02.059  
-He won't have any say.
-[Rivers] He doesn't.

206
00:10:02.143 --> 00:10:05.980  
So I... [chuckles] I'll do it
just based on what we've got to do

207
00:10:06.063 --> 00:10:08.315  
to get him out in December
and keep him D-I eligible.

208
00:10:08.399 --> 00:10:11.527 
{\an8}Tomorrow night.
'cause you're gonna be all excited.

209
00:10:11.611 --> 00:10:13.112 
{\an8}you're gonna go to class. have tutoring...

210
00:10:13.195 --> 00:10:14.656 
{\an8}Your friends are here.
you're gonna have football.

211
00:10:14.739 --> 00:10:16.991 
{\an8}you're gonna go to dinner.
and you're gonna be sitting in dinner.

212
00:10:17.074 --> 00:10:18.075  
You're gonna be chilling. hanging out.

213
00:10:18.159 --> 00:10:20.870  
and then you're gonna forget
about this class.

214
00:10:20.953 --> 00:10:22.622  
You know I'm gonna cut up at dinner.

215
00:10:22.705 --> 00:10:25.750  
You've got to remember
that you have this class at 9:00.

216
00:10:25.833 --> 00:10:26.709  
-All right.
-'Cause you miss it.

217
00:10:26.793 --> 00:10:27.669  
you're gonna get dropped.

218
00:10:28.878 --> 00:10:32.214 
{\an8}You have no more leeway.
My magic wand has already been waved.

219
00:10:32.298 --> 00:10:34.967 
{\an8}So there's no more fairy dust.
There's no more magic.

220
00:10:35.051 --> 00:10:37.219  
It's now on Isaiah Wright to get it done.

221
00:10:37.303 --> 00:10:39.055  
All right. But I ain't worried about it.

222
00:10:40.056 --> 00:10:41.348  
[Wagner] You're still here.

223
00:10:41.432 --> 00:10:43.976  
-That's where we gotta be for you.
-[Isaiah] Okay.

224
00:10:44.060 --> 00:10:46.520  
'Cause these offers
that we have right now...

225
00:10:46.937 --> 00:10:49.940  
-will disappear if this changes to May.
-Yeah. Okay.

226
00:10:50.191 --> 00:10:51.608  
[Wagner] <i>They are a group of kids.</i>

227
00:10:51.693 --> 00:10:54.987  
<i>I just think it's gonna be</i>
<i>a stressful semester</i>

228
00:10:55.071 --> 00:10:58.407  
<i>because there's a lot of them that are</i>
<i>on track to get out in December.</i>

229
00:10:58.490 --> 00:11:00.201  
<i>Maybe more than normal.</i>

230
00:11:00.284 --> 00:11:03.245 
{\an8}And I think there's the whole distraction
