445
00:21:42.551 --> 00:21:45.804  
<i>He went against our first D last night.</i>
<i>and he did pretty dang good.</i>

446
00:21:45.887 --> 00:21:49.850  
That's fine. I can live with that.
I can live with that.

447
00:21:49.933 --> 00:21:51.477  
[Wood] <i>Vijay wanted to compete.</i>

448
00:21:51.560 --> 00:21:53.061  
<i>Some people get scared off by that.</i>

449
00:21:53.144 --> 00:21:54.270  
<i>"I heard you got</i>
<i>a Division I quarterback."</i>

450
00:21:54.355 --> 00:21:55.731  
