458
00:22:10.662 --> 00:22:12.914  
Let's keep building off of that.
We're not where we need to be.

459
00:22:12.998 --> 00:22:14.333  
Let's keep building off of that
so we can get

460
00:22:14.416 --> 00:22:15.501  
where you need to be next week.

461
00:22:15.584 --> 00:22:17.002  
and where you need to be
the week after that.

462
00:22:17.085 --> 00:22:19.505  
And you keep doing what you're doing.
All right? Good?

463
00:22:19.588 --> 00:22:21.047  
Qs on three. One. two. three...

464
00:22:21.131 --> 00:22:22.215  
[all] Qs.

465
00:22:22.298 --> 00:22:24.843  
