It's not a stick.

466
00:22:24.926 --> 00:22:26.136  
Gotta make sure I see that.

467
00:22:26.219 --> 00:22:28.054  
You guys. you gotta know that stuff.

468
00:22:28.138 --> 00:22:30.181  
You can't just wait. Gotta know it.

469
00:22:30.265 --> 00:22:31.266  
Vijay.

470
00:22:31.349 --> 00:22:32.851  
[Wood] Can't do that. Can't do that.

471
00:22:32.934 --> 00:22:34.603  
Jones has got some good edge players.

472
00:22:34.686 --> 00:22:36.605  
You're gonna have to do
a great job blocking 'em.

473
00:22:36.688 --> 00:22:39.315  
[Buddy] <i>You're gonna be in charge</i>
