487
00:23:11.139 --> 00:23:13.475  
I didn't play football
till about sixth grade.

488
00:23:13.559 --> 00:23:16.227  
I was playing baseball.
That's where it really all started at.

489
00:23:16.311 --> 00:23:19.565  
<i>I threw harder than almost everybody.</i>
<i>The fastest I ever thrown was 93.</i>

490
00:23:19.648 --> 00:23:23.401  
So I was like. "Okay. might as well
try football and be a quarterback."

491
00:23:23.485 --> 00:23:26.404  
I ain't get no. uh.
D-I offer or anything like that.

492
00:23:26.488 --> 00:23:27.781  
It was mainly all JUCO.

493
00:23:27.864 --> 00:23:31.201  
I thought I was better.
Well. I know I'm better than that.

494
00:23:31.284 --> 00:23:34.579  
So I just came to East Mississippi
