512
00:24:23.629 --> 00:24:24.462  
All right.

513
00:24:25.797 --> 00:24:28.008  
-Do you have a notebook?
-Nope. [sighs]

514
00:24:28.091 --> 00:24:30.301  
[Wagner] <i>Okay. we're gonna make</i>
<i>a notebook right now.</i>

515
00:24:30.969 --> 00:24:33.304  
And then next week.
you're gonna have the notebook

516
00:24:33.388 --> 00:24:34.472  
