517
00:24:34.556 --> 00:24:36.307  
[Tim] Mm-hmm-hmm...

518
00:24:36.391 --> 00:24:38.101  
-Yes?
-Yeah. I heard you.

519
00:24:38.977 --> 00:24:40.395  
I just need me some rest.

520
00:24:40.478 --> 00:24:41.730  
Go home and lay down and rest.

521
00:24:41.813 --> 00:24:43.857  
[Wagner] Come in here.
we're gonna make a notebook.

522
00:24:44.691 --> 00:24:46.109  
[clicks tongue and sighs]

523
00:24:47.402 --> 00:24:48.987  
[Wagner] You want one with a penguin?

524
00:24:49.070 --> 00:24:51.823  
-What are your classes?
-[Tim grunts]

525
00:24:51.907 --> 00:24:54.743  
Miss Mullins for human and...
develop growth.

526
00:24:54.826 --> 00:24:57.871  
And. um. Ms. Castleberry for. uh...

527
00:24:58.997 --> 00:25:00.206  
Just put Castleberry.

528
00:25:01.249 --> 00:25:02.834  
It was like a. uh...

529
00:25:02.918 --> 00:25:03.877  
[unzipping]

530
00:25:05.796 --> 00:25:07.881  
-[Wagner] Tim?
-[Tim] What up?

531
00:25:07.964 --> 00:25:10.592  
-[Wagner] What is this?
-[chuckles]

532
00:25:10.676 --> 00:25:13.970  
Tim. this is a mess.
I need you to do better.

533
00:25:15.430 --> 00:25:17.348  
<i>I don't know a whole lot about him.</i>

534
00:25:17.432 --> 00:25:21.562  
<i>Went to Louisville out of high school</i>
<i>and then came here from Louisville.</i>

535
00:25:21.645 --> 00:25:24.314  
<i>I think he is a sweet. sweet guy.</i>

536
00:25:24.397 --> 00:25:28.526  
But sometimes. when I ask him something.
I have to say it. like. three times

537
00:25:28.610 --> 00:25:32.447  
because he's just... not even...

538
00:25:32.530 --> 00:25:35.784  
It's like he's not even aware
of where he is and what he's doing.

539
00:25:36.492 --> 00:25:38.829  
Okay. next week. we're knockin' out
all of our homework...

540
00:25:38.912 --> 00:25:40.205  
-Listen to me.
-I hear you.

541
00:25:40.914 --> 00:25:42.290  
Look at me.

542
00:25:45.627 --> 00:25:47.003  
It's turned all the way up.

543
00:25:47.588 --> 00:25:50.298  
[chuckles] Look. okay? [stammers]

544
00:25:51.299 --> 00:25:52.383  
See?

545
00:25:52.467 --> 00:25:54.970  
[chuckles] Next week.
we're doing all the home...

546
00:25:55.053 --> 00:25:57.180  
Look at me and focus on what I'm saying.

547
00:25:57.263 --> 00:25:59.015  
Yeah. I'mma get the homework.
notes. and everything.

548
00:25:59.099 --> 00:26:01.059  
Next week. we're doing
all the homework and quizzes for math.

549
00:26:01.142 --> 00:26:05.438  
and I want all... [stammers]
The three history quizzes done.

550
00:26:05.521 --> 00:26:06.522  
All right.

551
00:26:08.441 --> 00:26:10.443  
I heard you. Miss Brittany. I promise you.

552
00:26:10.652 --> 00:26:12.320  
Now I need to get water. I'm thirsty.

553
00:26:12.403 --> 00:26:15.323  
I been here... held hostage.
Like I'm in a jail.

554
00:26:15.406 --> 00:26:16.742  
[Wagner laughing]

555
00:26:19.995 --> 00:26:21.121  
Oh... [sighs]

556
00:26:27.085 --> 00:26:28.920  
What's going on. man?
How you doing today?

557
00:26:30.463 --> 00:26:32.507  
[Tim] <i>I was at</i>
<i>the University of Louisville.</i>

558
00:26:32.590 --> 00:26:33.842  
<i>but I had got into trouble.</i>

559
00:26:33.925 --> 00:26:34.926  
Uh...

560
00:26:36.344 --> 00:26:38.138  
It's a long story. but...

561
00:26:38.763 --> 00:26:41.558  
Somebody had said
I had a gun in my dorm. so...

562
00:26:42.225 --> 00:26:44.602  
they checked my room.
but they ain't find no gun.

563
00:26:44.686 --> 00:26:46.897  
[stammers] <i>I had a meeting</i>
<i>with the student dean.</i>

564
00:26:46.980 --> 00:26:49.357  
<i>Went over and. um. she said...</i>

565
00:26:50.358 --> 00:26:52.318  
"She don't feel comfortable
about you on the campus. so...

566
00:26:52.402 --> 00:26:54.529  
you can stay and get charged
or leave and go home."

567
00:26:55.196 --> 00:26:57.741  
So I packed my stuff the same day.
got on a bus. and went to Birmingham.

568
00:26:58.366 --> 00:27:02.370  
I need to keep going. 'cause in my family.
I'm the first one to make it.

569
00:27:02.453 --> 00:27:04.414  
I had a lot of brothers play basketball
and football.

570
00:27:04.497 --> 00:27:06.374  
and they ain't too much make it. so...

571
00:27:06.457 --> 00:27:07.500  
they dropped out of school.

572
00:27:07.583 --> 00:27:10.170  
So they were on me tough
to keep me motivated a lot.

573
00:27:10.253 --> 00:27:12.005  
and tell me to keep on pushing myself.

574
00:27:17.928 --> 00:27:20.764  
