576
00:27:25.268 --> 00:27:26.269  
First game.

577
00:27:27.312 --> 00:27:28.521  
And he can't do it.

578
00:27:29.022 --> 00:27:32.108  
Watch. And this one's even worse. Okay?

579
00:27:32.192 --> 00:27:35.820  
He's the backup to the backup.
That guy can't play.

580
00:27:36.029 --> 00:27:37.697  
We're bad at this right now.

581
00:27:38.198 --> 00:27:42.160  
So many freshmen that have no clue.

582
00:27:43.453 --> 00:27:46.956  
That. right there?
That. right there. is just mental.

583
00:27:47.457 --> 00:27:50.919  
This is the mentality
that we have right now as a team.

584
00:27:51.002 --> 00:27:51.837  
That. right there.

585
00:27:53.171 --> 00:27:56.299  
They're not very coachable right now.
I don't know what it is.

586
00:27:57.968 --> 00:27:59.260  
So what do we do?

587
00:28:00.011 --> 00:28:02.138  
-What do we do?
-Keep working.

588
00:28:02.222 --> 00:28:04.682  
Don't get frustrated over one deal.
Just keep grinding.

589
00:28:04.766 --> 00:28:06.392  
-We gotta keep going.
-[Buddy] But this is everyday deal.

590
00:28:06.476 --> 00:28:09.062  
-Well. but I mean--
-[Buddy] This ain't a one-day deal.

591
00:28:09.145 --> 00:28:11.940  
We've not blocked. and that's...
This is my responsibility.

592
00:28:12.023 --> 00:28:14.400  
[Wood stammers]
I have to do it every day. I get it.

593
00:28:14.484 --> 00:28:16.069  
-It is an everyday deal.
-[sighs]

594
00:28:16.652 --> 00:28:17.653  
You gotta keep working.

595
00:28:17.738 --> 00:28:19.781  
I don't think there's anything
other to do than that.

596
00:28:19.865 --> 00:28:24.870  
But the problem is. right now.
our demeanor is not very good. Period.

597
00:28:25.829 --> 00:28:28.373  
Young guys. do y'all want to use these?

598
00:28:28.915 --> 00:28:31.667  
-In the first game? Huh?
-[player] I'll use it. It'll be faster.

599
00:28:31.752 --> 00:28:34.587  
Okay. you okay to do that?
You gotta get it to... Can you read?

600
00:28:34.670 --> 00:28:35.671  
-[player] Uh-huh.
-[all laugh]

601
00:28:35.756 --> 00:28:39.300  
I mean. can you see that?
Is it too small?

602
00:28:39.384 --> 00:28:40.844  
[player] No. we had that in high school.

603
00:28:40.927 --> 00:28:46.141  
[Buddy] Get red. red. red. red.
red. red. red. No. red only.

604
00:28:46.224 --> 00:28:48.894  
Red. I got six.
No. I got the six. dummy!

605
00:28:48.977 --> 00:28:50.686  
Am I... am I speaking French?

606
00:28:50.771 --> 00:28:53.606  
-I got number. you got color!
-Oh. we ain't communicate that.

607
00:28:53.689 --> 00:28:55.650  
[Buddy] I'm gonna communicate it.
Here we go.

608
00:28:55.734 --> 00:28:58.695  
Right. right. right. right. right.
right. right. right. right. right!

609
00:28:59.195 --> 00:29:00.739  
That's how they gonna be in the game. too.

610
00:29:02.032 --> 00:29:06.369  
Arguing. "No. dummy. your left hand."
"White."

611
00:29:06.452 --> 00:29:08.038  
Here we go! Red.

612
00:29:09.205 --> 00:29:11.291  
Eight! Eight!

613
00:29:12.417 --> 00:29:14.294  
-Please don't hold 'em both up.
-I didn't.

614
00:29:14.377 --> 00:29:15.503  
[Buddy] Eight. Red-Eight.

615
00:29:16.254 --> 00:29:19.715  
Hey. dickhead here. he's gotta
figure out what we... [stutters]

616
00:29:19.800 --> 00:29:22.593  
He can't hold up both arms
and go. "Take a guess."

617
00:29:22.677 --> 00:29:25.972  
[stutters] It's right. it's right!
It ain't red. it ain't white. it's right!

618
00:29:26.056 --> 00:29:28.141  
<i>I mean. it's... it's tough. man.</i>

619
00:29:28.224 --> 00:29:31.394  
<i>It's just. uh...</i>
<i>you want 'em to get better so fast.</i>

620
00:29:31.477 --> 00:29:33.604  
<i>and... and it takes a little time.</i>

621
00:29:33.688 --> 00:29:36.399  
I want to blow up so bad.
and I just wanna...

622
00:29:36.482 --> 00:29:39.945  
You know. I just wanna. uh.
let the expletives fly. you know.

623
00:29:40.028 --> 00:29:43.156  
[stammers] But we're working
very hard to. uh...

624
00:29:43.239 --> 00:29:46.367  
to make sure that. uh.
we do things the right way.

625
00:29:46.451 --> 00:29:50.496  
[stammers] And. uh. it's very challenging.

